{"tid":147508,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消防員爬電視牆關a片　不慎摔落殉職","createTime":"2017-03-08T01:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T14:07:06.000Z","uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b5b7a24a31e8ac6bcc46ed95ce12f3ab7b2a34e","tid":147508,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:50:55.000Z","msg":"墨西哥一名消防人員岡札拉茲(Alvaro Jimenez Gonzalez)，日前在一處公路上爬上電視牆，企圖關掉正在播放的A片，但岡札拉茲卻不慎失足摔落，因公殉職。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，在聖安多尼奧(San Antonio)地區，有民眾發現一處公路上的電視牆，正播放著A片，並將這景象拍下上傳網路。消防員發現後，擔心A片會使用路人分心，造成更多意外，因此出動岡札拉茲處理。岡札拉茲企圖爬上電視牆，關掉A片，卻沒想到一失足而摔下，最後不幸因公殉職。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n報導也指出，公路電視牆很可能遭駭客入侵，才會出現A片。而當地消防局也對岡札拉茲的死表示哀悼，當局也要求電視牆業者加強防駭客的管理。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"629355395a0979434f467291a72a73e24e35b2b1","tid":147508,"uid":55120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:53:32.000Z","msg":"又關施旖婕事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db045d0884e61287ad92f4bc7e63ef8a4d818e4","tid":147508,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:56:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jJkuCzgg7fo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjJkuCzgg7fo&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=a43c9018\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jJkuCzgg7fo</a>"},{"pid":"149986c561deb9008ccf197b30d4320dc2ea6b8e","tid":147508,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:07:06.000Z","msg":"呢個就係奇聞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}